OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering daytime showers will ease
OL,7,Fthis evening leaving a dry night with
OL,8,Fclear spells for a while. However,
OL,9,Fcloud and patchy rain will move in
OL,10,Ffrom the west during the early hours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FSome early brightness in the
OL,13,Ffar east, otherwise a cloudy day with
OL,14,Foccasional rain and drizzle. The rain
OL,15,Fturning heavy at times, especially
OL,16,Flater. Fog patches forming, and winds
OL,17,Fstrengthening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
