OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FWet
OL,6,Fand windy for a time on Wednesday with
OL,7,Fscattered showers following on
OL,8,FThursday, before turning drier and
OL,9,Fbrighter on Friday. Feeling warmer
OL,10,Fthan of late, especially in any
OL,11,Fsunshine.
